{"tid":855334,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"婚後會同奶奶住???","createTime":"2018-10-10T03:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T15:22:35.000Z","uid":130955,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"500912c33bdf4595ec69b61a22336a6846ea693d","tid":855334,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"假設男友係單親&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n如果你地結婚<br />\n究竟會唔會同埋奶奶住?<br />\n<br />\n唔同佢住就係唔孝順?"},{"pid":"ba30af815a03cb157aeda170c9a2cbb063b70cc3","tid":855334,"uid":21423,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"305ca4f117d833c53039a6b9cc13bb9ee9a4cc3a","tid":855334,"uid":164863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"相見好同住難"},{"pid":"16c9e4ea7978acea0dc645aa357119c7299222fa","tid":855334,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"開個post 係為左睇下究竟有幾多人真係會接受到同奶奶住"},{"pid":"10218e3cedfcb2c1a310d6c9d1d70b3d0286b055","tid":855334,"uid":54597,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"千其唔好"},{"pid":"96b89e0e99d9ebf20340e355289bc5569be4875e","tid":855334,"uid":33730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"相見好同住難<br />\n一齊住既話成間屋特別係廚房廁所都係戰場<br />\n千祈唔好做傻事"},{"pid":"6997fa9b3b618ad067ff4acc3889724b57d2858d","tid":855334,"uid":57554,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"盡量唔好比你太太同呀媽見太多<br />\n有能力嘅點都要搬出去住，租都好<br />\n冇能力嘅，真係要結嘅，你就預左自己係磨心。<br />\n有咩衝突，就出黎頂左佢，無辦法，冇人叫你冇能力就結婚，你處理得唔好就兩邊都係罪人。<br />\n<br />\n你太太同你夾，唔代表同你呀媽夾"},{"pid":"2287080f521b26bb0b7f1af61ca768cc11712fdc","tid":855334,"uid":144843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40d9aaffb2d2627eccbbc76a2b7b342e5394a23f","tid":855334,"uid":199692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:20:28.000Z","msg":"我係過來人，<br />\n<br />\n你千其唔好累兩個女人。<br />\n<br />\n一係無能力有自己地方就唔好結婚，累人個女。"},{"pid":"aaa4030cda8e94116bd5e576e2d66e31bd1baddf","tid":855334,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"我而家都陷入兩難狀態<br />\n一開口同阿媽講搬出去住佢發癲話唔比<br />\n而家屋又搵左就黎搬入去住<br />\n唔知以後婆媳關係可以差成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf1775d9d83af2e9cef674587a5acf0c8599833","tid":855334,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:25:40.000Z","msg":"女人好古惑, 佢地夾呢, 當你阿4做人情討好對方, &quot;喂老公同奶奶搞掂佢&quot;, &quot;喂阿仔同新抱搞掂佢&quot;<br />\n,就會洗死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夾仲HIHI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人x2=煩, 最好唔好同一間屋有女人x2 or above<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有家姐, 阿妹既人就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02eca5ec4f72cf3f428e9b66af1d4b043646c3e","tid":855334,"uid":19485,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好相處一齊住一定有問題<br />\n唔講話性格夾唔夾, 生活習慣呢啲大問題<br />\n細問題到用邊隻洗衣粉洗衫你都可能會有自己意見<br />\n呢啲小問題積埋積埋以後好易睇唔順眼架<br />\n如果另一半係單親<br />\n你寧願租/買啲近佢既地方都唔好一齊住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:過來人, 以前都唔信, 結果一齊住唔夠一年搬咗"},{"pid":"749422e56c0dc8d3b9936fced8d0494a02af2622","tid":855334,"uid":199692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02eca5ec4f72cf3f428e9b66af1d4b043646c3e","tid":855334,"uid":19485,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好相處一齊住一定有問題<br />\n唔講話性格夾唔夾, 生活習慣呢啲大問題<br />\n細問題到用邊隻洗衣粉洗衫你都可能會有自己意見<br />\n呢啲小問題積埋積埋以後好易睇唔順眼架<br />\n如果另一半係單親<br />\n你寧願租/買啲近佢既地方都唔好一齊住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm