<br />\n所以先上黎問問各位<br />\n最近因為哩樣好爭扎<br />\n雖然唔係拍左好耐拖<br />\n但我覺得一日唔唸清楚，繼續行都係死"},{"pid":"c71d092e69349ca35db2b337996077746d212cbf","tid":855334,"uid":12219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"一定要搬出去住<br />\n結左婚就係要2人世界有自己既生活<br />\n仲同屋企人住既話不如唔好結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我以前成日去ex屋企訓我都覺得唔慣<br />\n始終有外人係度一定唔會好似自己屋企咁舒服"},{"pid":"d0e2dc91f1206fb6d96255a894c6dad87f7613ea","tid":855334,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500912c33bdf4595ec69b61a22336a6846ea693d","tid":855334,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"假設男友係單親&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n如果你地結婚<br />\n究竟會唔會同埋奶奶住?<br />\n<br />\n唔同佢住就係唔孝順?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:08:18.000Z","msg":"死都唔會一齊住 寧願唔結"},{"pid":"77244966da94e752c6704fe59f28b150c8de2d6b","tid":855334,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71d092e69349ca35db2b337996077746d212cbf","tid":855334,"uid":12219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"一定要搬出去住<br />\n結左婚就係要2人世界有自己既生活<br />\n仲同屋企人住既話不如唔好結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我以前成日去ex屋企訓我都覺得唔慣<br />\n始終有外人係度一定唔會好似自己屋企咁舒服"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"佢呀媽點好?"},{"pid":"c7221e84150133c877f73c7c2087e88534376a11","tid":855334,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77244966da94e752c6704fe59f28b150c8de2d6b","tid":855334,"uid":130955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71d092e69349ca35db2b337996077746d212cbf","tid":855334,"uid":12219,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"一定要搬出去住<br />\n結左婚就係要2人世界有自己既生活<br />\n仲同屋企人住既話不如唔好結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal